<title>Aw Hung Lengin Lalpa</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chi gimthei lungkhamna lei ahin,
 Lungkham luonthi tawh Nang ka hun sam;
 Ka Lalpa'n ei umpih zing inla,
 Nam gimthei, liengvai pak banga lun ding.

[V2]
 Aw, hung lengin Lalpa ka hun ngai,
 Kalvari-a nei hehpihna chu;
 Ka chungu-ah puon bang hung zakin,
 Nam gimthei, liengvai pak banga pak ding,

[V3]
 2. A haksatna munah um mah leng,
 Lalpa, Nanglo midang sam puo'ngka;
 Senlai nau bang ka kahna gamah,
 Nam tin lungmawl lakah Nang hung vakin.

[V4]
 3. Gitlohnan ei naih zel mahleu le,
 Thihna luiguom ah leng mah leng le;
 Lalpa, Na Thagau in ei puiin,
 Nei hehpihna thing banga hung pak ding.

[V5]
 4. Gimthei mah leng Aw van Lallukhuk,
 Gitloh gal laka semgim te ding;
 Na gam vanga ka gimtheih nate,
 Ka Pa anga pak gimlim in a pak.</lyrics>
</song>